e there to make sure clients get up on time, make sure medication is taken on schedule and clients get to appointments on time.</p><p>Experience: one year experience working with seniors, four years experience working with children/adults in a residential setting.</p><p style="height:6px;"></p><p>We are a Equal Employment Opportunity.</p><br /><br /><div style="text-align:left;padding-bottom: 20px;"><a href="/frca-apply/bjtg51" id="ApplyBottomLink" target="_blank" class="bigBlueButtonLink" rel="nofollow" onclick="javascript:setTimeout(&quot;window.location.href = &#39;/post-resume?jid=bjtg51&#39;;&quot;,1500); return true;">Go to apply&nbsp;<img src="/Images/applyarrow.png" height="21x;" width="16px;" alt="" /></a></div></div></div></div><div style="background-color: #fcfcfc; max-width: 400px;" class="sideBar"><div style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-left:5px;"><h4 style="padding-bottom:7px;">Similar Jobs</h4><p style="padding-bottom:4px;"><a href="/job/bjepe6/caregivers-home-caregiver-wayne-pa-19087" rel="nofollow" onclick="ga(&#39;send&#39;, &#39;event&#39;, &#39;Links&#39;, &#39;JobToJob&#39;, &#39;0&#39;);">Caregiver - Home Health Aide - CNA - Direct Support Staff</a><br/><span style="font-size:small" class="colorLocation">Wayne, PA</span><span style="font-size:small;color:black"> - caregivers, home, caregiver, cna, health aide, hha,...</span></p><p style="padding-bottom:4px;"><a href="/job/bjgnyt/church-caregivers-home-hha-glen-mills-pa" rel="nofollow" onclick="ga(&#39;send&#39;, &#39;event&#39;, &#39;Links&#39;, &#39;JobToJob&#39;, &#39;1&#39;);">Caregiver - Home Health Aids- CNA- Direct Support Staff</a><br/><span style="font-size:small" class="colorLocation">Glen Mills, PA</span><span style="font-size:small;color:black"> - church, caregivers, home, home care, caregiver,...</span></p><p style="padding-bottom:4px;"><a href="/job/bi2cv8/hha-cna-caregiver-home-philadelphia-pa" rel="nofollow" onclick="ga(&#39;send&#39;, &#39;event&#39;, &#39;Links